parts.text:
Here is a description of the video.

The video is a tutorial on how to create AI hyperlapses. The video opens with a shot of a phone displaying a short video of a table with a glass of water and a small skull on it. The narrator then explains that AI hyperlapses are currently going viral on YouTube and Instagram. The video then shows several examples of AI hyperlapses, including a statue of a woman and a lion, a church dome, and a statue of a woman and child. The narrator then shows how to create these videos using a phone and computer.
